  "description": "The (5,8) Fibonacci torus approximates the golden ratio — P/Q approaches φ as you climb the Fibonacci sequence. The pqScale at (5,8) is 0.962, producing coupling asymmetry that never fully resolves into a periodic pattern. macroKnot=0.5 sits the matrix exactly halfway between Torus and Solomon: the golden winding bleeds into the two-ring linked architecture. LFO2 on filter at 0.05 Hz, LFO1 on braid depth at 0.02 Hz — two slow modulations at incommensurate rates, a micro-polyrhythm in topology space. Legato glide carries the golden ratio through intervals.",
